{"tid":1531418,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[P牌]大家好, 我想分享下我睇小說的心得","createTime":"2019-09-02T08:12:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T08:14:00.000Z","uid":229986,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b338f4add47966d9676d46ee8bb09f2ebb25798","tid":1531418,"uid":229986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:12:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知點解呢排突然間 念返起以前睇過一本內地的小說, 叫<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">無限恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n其中一個章節呢就是講主角們和黃金面具的怪物戰鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知點解, 睇左成本小說, 我覺得呢到最深刻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到呢到呢, 個黃金面具怪物有個特性呢, 就係<span style=\"color: orange;\">戰鬥力會愈來愈高, 而且可以由其他生物吸能量轉化成分身(類似吸血鬼)<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>, <br />\n按照普通的打法呢, 就係一路拖住怪物, 一路搵盟友同埋念計去利用它的弱點(怕光, 唔可以斷糧)去集火打倒它<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(直接打打唔過),<br />\n個陣時呢, 原本主角可以按照返普通路線去打<br />\n但係呢, 主角就行左另一條路<br />\n就係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迫它瘋狂升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我個時心念, <br />\n下, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對面會愈黎愈打得, 又識得吸能量無限續, 點解幫它升級, 點解唔拖住他, 慢慢斷它食糧, 再係它最弱個陣組隊打敗它呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">原來對家識得分身補能量, 你永遠唔知道係咪真係可以斷糧拖住它<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">分身同本體的能量體係連埋一起的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,</span> <br />\n而且自己友升級慢, 又唔知道自己友可唔可以拖住那個時候, 拖得愈拖, 戰局其實愈不利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n主角利用左怪物的特點, <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">怪物的戰鬥力只可以上升唔可以下降, 而升左的話需要的能量愈多, 需要瘋狂吸其他生物的能量去維持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. <br />\n一路拖一路迫它升級, 強制提高它維持高戰鬥力的能量需要, 迫它瘋狂向其他生物下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">迫到它硬生生打緊個陣餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">不過呢個方法風險好高, 因為怪物戰鬥力高左, 一頂唔住就玩完<br />\n係個高風險打法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左呢段之外, 本小說其他部份都幾好睇, 我強烈推薦比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0be7515734fd50386d81dd8160a8ff8d7bca500b","tid":1531418,"uid":229986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"對唔住 放錯台了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟少開post, 唔識set 唔好意思"}]}